Feature: OrangeHRM Employee Management

  Scenario: Add and verify employees
   Scenario: Add employees and verify them in the employee list
    Given User is on OrangeHRM login page
    When User logs in with username "Admin" and password "admin123"
    And User navigates to the PIM module
    And User adds the following employees
      | FirstName | LastName  |
      | Alice     | Smith     |
      | Bob       | Johnson   |
      | Charlie   | Brown     |
    Then User verifies the employees are present in the list
    And User logs out of the application
